Package: conduitR
Title: R tools for metaproteomics analysis using conduit and conduit-GUI
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person(given ="Charlie", family ="Bayne", email = "baynec2@gmail.com",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description:
    conduitR provides tools for metaproteomic analysis. These tools
    power Conduit (snakemake workflow for metaproteomics) as well as Conduit-GUI
    (graphic interface to explore results from the Conduit workflow).
License: MIT + file LICENSE
